{"type":"article","id":6076,"title":"目前中国有多起激起&quot;爱国心&quot;的事件正在发酵：苹果丶火箭队丶杜兰特","uid":6003,"topics":[],"contents":"首先是火箭队<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/01Esi76.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/01Esi76.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/01Esi76.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n再来是杜兰特被扒出曾经在八月份转过达赖的言论<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/eI6LscR.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eI6LscR.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/eI6LscR.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n接着是苹果上架帮助香港&quot;暴徒&quot;的APP，曾经达到微博热搜第一，但目前已被撤，仍未平民怨。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ErTkpso.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ErTkpso.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ErTkpso.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/vTsHuPq.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vTsHuPq.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/vTsHuPq.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n我感觉火箭队莫雷事件会是一个历史转折点。<br>\n<br>\n火烧得越旺，就会有越多人觉得不对劲。<br>\n<br>\n我十分怀疑杜兰特八月份的言论是那些愤愤不平的火箭球迷扒的，看来铁拳果然是有效的。","date":"2019-10-06","agreeCount":17,"discussionCount":0}